00:54.788 --> 00:56.184
<i>much less a franchise.</i>

00:56.319 --> 00:59.453
[anacheka] <i>Marvel's so stupid.</i>

00:59.589 --> 01:01.389
<i>Angalia, we know the title
of this thing.</i>

01:01.524 --> 01:03.190
<i>So, I know
what you're wondering.</i>

01:03.325 --> 01:04.393
<i>How are we gonna do this</i>

01:04.528 --> 01:07.765
<i>without dishonoring
Logan's memory?</i>

01:07.900 --> 01:09.266
<i>Nami nitakuambia how.</i>

01:10.033 --> 01:11.369
<i>We're not.</i>

01:11.505 --> 01:12.897
[♪ romantic music plays,
The Platters "Only You"]

01:13.032 --> 01:15.036
<i>I'm gonna let you in
on a little secret.</i>

01:15.171 --> 01:17.366
<i>Wolverine is not dead.</i>

01:17.501 --> 01:20.646
<i>Sure, it made for a perfect
ending to a very sad story.</i>

01:20.781 --> 01:21.805
<i>Lakini that's not how</i>

01:21.941 --> 01:23.906
<i>regenerative healing
factors work.</i>

01:24.042 --> 01:25.216
<i>You think
I wanna be out here</i>

01:25.352 --> 01:27.343
<i>in beautiful downtown
North Dakota,</i>

01:27.478 --> 01:30.586
<i>digging up the one and only
Wolverine? No, thank you.</i>

01:30.721 --> 01:33.191
<i>Lakini the fate of
my entire world is at stake.</i>

01:33.326 --> 01:34.683
<i>He may not
be living his best life,</i>

01:34.819 --> 01:37.025
<i>but he sure as hell ain't</i>

01:37.161 --> 01:38.757
<i>- dead.</i>
- [metal clanks]

01:41.660 --> 01:43.168
[crow cawing in distance]

01:43.702 --> 01:44.697
Bingo.

01:45.539 --> 01:46.534
Yahtzee.

01:47.838 --> 01:49.031
[anapumua]

01:49.777 --> 01:52.672
Yes, yes, yes, yes, yes.

01:56.341 --> 01:57.314
Damn it!

01:58.184 --> 02:01.076
- Son of a bitch!
- [metal clangs]

02:02.721 --> 02:04.119
You...

02:04.255 --> 02:06.021
- [shovel snaps]
- [kupiga kelele]

02:06.156 --> 02:09.358
Christ. Motherfucker!

02:09.494 --> 02:11.028
- My world is fuck...
- [♪ wimbo unasimama]

02:11.164 --> 02:13.962
[laughs, snorts]
That was weird.

02:14.098 --> 02:15.267
I'm much calmer now.

02:15.402 --> 02:16.727
