02:26.143 --> 02:27.645
Lakini it's good to see ya.

02:27.781 --> 02:30.816
I gotta be honest,
I've always wanted
to ride with you, Log.

02:30.951 --> 02:32.140
You and me getting into it.

02:32.276 --> 02:35.911
Deadpool and Wolverine
just fuckin' shit up.

02:36.047 --> 02:39.015
Can you imagine the fun,
the chaos...

02:39.518 --> 02:40.523
the residuals?

02:41.459 --> 02:42.657
