- Smashturbating?

07:34.180 --> 07:35.445
I'm sorry, what...
what was that?

07:35.580 --> 07:38.880
No, I'm sorry. That...
That's when you get those toy,

07:39.015 --> 07:40.251
Hulk hands, right?

07:40.387 --> 07:41.724
And then you just, you look
down, and you just...

07:43.027 --> 07:45.488
you brace yourself,
and you ravage the midsection.

07:45.624 --> 07:47.223
- Pinch the... Yeah. Sawa.
- I get it. Okay, thank you.

07:47.359 --> 07:49.158
- The picture's painted.
- You get the gist.

07:49.294 --> 07:51.631
Uh, what exactly
brings you here today?

07:51.766 --> 07:54.829
Why am I... Wow. Sawa. Uh...

07:54.964 --> 07:56.365
I... I care.

07:56.500 --> 07:59.434
I know I turn everything
into a joke, but I...

08:01.306 --> 08:04.175
I care, and I wanna use
that feeling...

08:05.009 --> 08:07.315
for something important.

08:07.451 --> 08:08.649
I... I wanna matter.

08:08.784 --> 08:11.313
[♪ kucheza muziki makini]

08:11.448 --> 08:13.415
I need to show my girl
that I matter.

08:14.719 --> 08:16.119
And...

08:16.254 --> 08:17.424
Unajua,
I feel like I'm wasting

08:17.560 --> 08:18.528
the good stuff here.

08:18.664 --> 08:19.855
Is the man not gonna
be joining us?

08:19.991 --> 08:20.926
- The man?
- Yeah.

08:21.061 --> 08:23.096
I should save this
if he's gonna...

08:23.232 --> 08:25.136
Uh, as far as you're concerned
right now, I'm the man.

08:25.272 --> 08:26.800
- Hapana.
- The man is me.

08:26.936 --> 08:29.800
I am the man
in this circumstance.

08:29.936 --> 08:31.033
- Mm.
- He doesn't do

08:31.168 --> 08:32.638
this kind of thing anymore.

08:32.773 --> 08:33.708
- Cameos?
- Meetings.

08:33.844 --> 08:35.375
- Meetings.
- Entry-level meetings.

08:35.510 --> 08:36.247
Entry-level?

08:36.382 --> 08:38.207
Aren't you the chauffeur...

08:38.343 --> 08:40.549
- maybe?
- I... Common misconception.

08:40.685 --> 08:41.911
- Sawa.
- I did begin my career

08:42.046 --> 08:43.717
as Mr. Stark's driver.

08:43.853 --> 08:44.885
- Sawa.
- Quickly pivoted to...

08:45.021 --> 08:46.315
- Chauffeur.
- ...the Head of Security.

08:46.450 --> 08:48.316
The Head of...
Of course, yes, yes, yes.

08:48.452 --> 08:51.354
And why I am vetting
your resume.

08:51.490 --> 08:53.762
You seem to have left out
whether or not you had

08:53.897 --> 08:55.495
any experience
as a member of a team.

08:55.631 --> 08:56.599
Could you maybe add

08:56.735 --> 08:57.800
a little bit
of perspective there?

08:57.935 --> 09:00.061
Oh. No, yes, of course.
I was Special Forces...

09:00.197 --> 09:01.129
- Sawa.
- ...but I was...

09:01.264 --> 09:02.801
Mainly, I was team leader...

09:02.936 --> 09:04.104
founder, really, of X-Force.

09:04.239 --> 09:06.069
Sadly, they... they all
perished in action though.

09:06.205 --> 09:07.436
Oh. How exactly
did that happen?

09:07.571 --> 09:09.679
Well, the police say gravity,
but if...

09:09.815 --> 09:11.107
Just between us,
they didn't test well

09:11.242 --> 09:12.648
- in the focus group.
- I see.

09:12.783 --> 09:14.382
- Particularly Cable.
- X-Force.

09:14.517 --> 09:15.486
Whoa, whoa, whoa.

09:15.622 --> 09:16.553
Angalia, I can see
this isn't going well.

09:16.689 --> 09:17.851
Please stop writing.
Angalia, I... I...

09:17.987 --> 09:20.053
I'm just...
I wanna be an Avenger.

09:21.657 --> 09:23.452
I wanna be an Avenger.

09:25.192 --> 09:26.992
Why do you wanna be
an Avenger?

09:27.128 --> 09:28.563
Look around you.
I mean, they're the...

09:28.699 --> 09:29.994
they're the best of the best.

09:30.130 --> 09:32.059
And... And what
they do matters.

09:32.195 --> 09:34.496
I need to be an Avenger.

09:34.632 --> 09:36.967
Sir, my girl
has kinda had it
with my shtick,

09:37.103 --> 09:38.303
and I... if I don't, unajua,

09:38.438 --> 09:41.140
turn things around and
do something with my "gifts,"

09:41.276 --> 09:42.906
sidhani it's gonna
really work out for me,

09:43.042 --> 09:44.374
and I wouldn't blame her.

09:45.544 --> 09:49.747
Avengers are a very unique
group of superheroes

09:49.883 --> 09:50.985
that stand for something

09:51.120 --> 09:53.648
more than just fighting
and wearing costumes.

09:53.784 --> 09:56.921
I mean, people look up to us.
Kids look up to us.

09:57.057 --> 09:58.156
- They--
- I'm sorry. "Us"?

09:58.291 --> 10:00.861
I wasn't aware
that you were an Avenger.

10:00.996 --> 10:01.927
Avengers-adjacent, technically.

10:02.063 --> 10:03.325
Oh, wow.
What's your superpower?

10:03.460 --> 10:06.004
Is it parallel parking?
I am so sorry.

10:06.139 --> 10:07.332
That was cruel.

10:07.467 --> 10:09.770
I lash out when I'm nervous.
Won't happen again.

10:09.905 --> 10:11.132
- Let's cut to the chase.
- Please.

10:11.268 --> 10:12.743
You just said moments ago

10:12.878 --> 10:15.207
