an Avenger because

10:15.808 --> 10:17.246
you need it.

10:17.381 --> 10:18.273
Yes, sir, I do.

10:18.408 --> 10:19.910
Lakini the Avengers
don't do the job

10:20.045 --> 10:21.377
because they need it.

10:21.513 --> 10:23.655
They do the job
because people need them.

10:24.820 --> 10:26.350
Do you see the distinction?

10:27.985 --> 10:29.551
Yes, sir.

10:30.428 --> 10:31.861
Please, Mr. Hogan.

10:31.996 --> 10:33.057
I don't wanna spend
the rest of my life

10:33.193 --> 10:35.392
