one-trick pony.

10:38.303 --> 10:39.297
Sawa.

10:40.165 --> 10:41.803
Oh, my God, you're standing.

10:41.939 --> 10:43.336
Yeah, now's the time
that we stand.

10:43.472 --> 10:44.399
Damn it.

10:44.535 --> 10:45.807
Now, the problem
might be that you're

10:45.943 --> 10:48.240
reaching a little...
little too high.

10:48.375 --> 10:50.812
Aim for the middle,
and you'll never miss.

10:50.948 --> 10:52.009
Right?
I think you got a good heart.

10:52.145 --> 10:53.949
I believe what you're saying.

10:54.084 --> 10:55.582
Lakini not everybody's
the world-saving type.

10:55.718 --> 10:57.348
I'm not, and I'm happy.

10:57.951 --> 10:59.724
Right? I found my place.

11:00.589 --> 11:01.990
Find your place.

11:02.892 --> 11:04.892
All right? Get back out there.

11:05.028 --> 11:06.493
- We'll keep an eye on you.
- Sawa.

11:06.628 --> 11:07.622
Good luck.

11:08.767 --> 11:11.228
- [Wade Wilson] Mm. Mm-hmm.
- Mm-hmm.

11:11.364 --> 11:13.865
Fetch the car.
I wanna hit Shake Shack.

11:14.001 --> 11:15.531
Rejection makes me hungy.

11:16.542 --> 11:17.970
- No, no. Please.
- No?

11:18.105 --> 11:19.605
- Yeah, no, no, no.
- Sawa.

11:19.740 --> 11:21.009
Okay, thank you.

11:22.947 --> 11:24.513
