that it sent shivers
down the Timeline.

23:48.427 --> 23:51.495
I am referring,
of course, to...

23:52.824 --> 23:56.599
Logan. Wolverine.

24:00.035 --> 24:02.464
[weakly] <i>Don't be
what they made you.</i>

24:03.400 --> 24:06.169
[♪ sentimental slow rock
kucheza muziki]

24:10.806 --> 24:12.241
[crying]

24:12.376 --> 24:15.112
<i>Ah, ndivyo hivyo
inavyojisikia...</i>

24:16.781 --> 24:17.983
[Deadpool] Logan.

24:18.716 --> 24:19.721
Of course.

24:20.387 --> 24:21.382
Logan.

24:23.018 --> 24:23.993
[Deadpool groans]

24:24.128 --> 24:25.558
[kupiga kelele] Logan?

24:25.694 --> 24:27.561
The guy with forks for hands?

24:27.697 --> 24:30.158
- That Wolverine?
- [device beeps]

24:30.293 --> 24:31.996
Yeah, I got it.
You can turn your

24:32.132 --> 24:34.338
retro graphics of death
off now. Make it stop.

24:34.474 --> 24:35.865
We're not doing it,
Bw. Wilson.

24:36.000 --> 24:37.233
We certainly can't stop it.

24:39.303 --> 24:40.301
[Deadpool]
How long have we got?

24:40.436 --> 24:42.940
In most cases,
couple thousand years.

24:43.076 --> 24:44.205
- Well, sweet.
- Well, most cases

24:44.341 --> 24:46.680
aren't fast enough.
Not for me.

24:46.815 --> 24:47.812
[Deadpool]
What does that mean?

24:47.948 --> 24:50.014
It means
that I have been tasked

24:50.150 --> 24:52.485
with overseeing
the end of your universe.

24:52.620 --> 24:53.722
And regardless of what

24:53.857 --> 24:55.387
the pencil pushers upstairs
would prefer,

24:55.522 --> 24:56.859
I will not

24:56.995 --> 25:00.223
waste my life watching it die
slowly of natural causes.

25:00.359 --> 25:02.390
We used to just prune
these things. Simple.

25:02.525 --> 25:04.392
Elegant. Efficient.
Lakini I'm told the TVA

25:04.527 --> 25:06.934
doesn't like to do that
anymore. Well, I do.

25:07.069 --> 25:08.769
And no matter what
my so-called superiors say,

25:08.905 --> 25:11.404
the multiverse does not
need a babysitter.

25:11.540 --> 25:13.110
We need a mercy killer.

25:13.245 --> 25:14.837
And in this instance,

25:14.973 --> 25:18.208
I am the mercy killer. Ha!

25:19.513 --> 25:20.518
[anacheka]

25:21.582 --> 25:22.652
[device beeps]

25:22.787 --> 25:24.281
[Deadpool] What in
the MacGuffin is that?

25:24.416 --> 25:26.649
[Bw. Kitendawili] That's
a Time Ripper, Bw. Wilson.

25:26.785 --> 25:28.317
An accelerant.

25:28.452 --> 25:31.055
Once completed,
it will allow me to destroy

25:31.191 --> 25:33.124
the spacetime matrix
of your universe.

25:33.259 --> 25:35.462
You see, I don't want
to work for the TVA.

25:35.597 --> 25:37.361
I want to be the TVA.

25:37.497 --> 25:40.129
And the first step involves
showing this organization

25:40.264 --> 25:42.033
how much more efficient
it can become.

25:42.169 --> 25:43.900
To wit, I will be
giving your universe

25:44.036 --> 25:46.468
a swift and compassionate end.

25:46.604 --> 25:48.109
Na usijali, your friends
won't feel a thing.

25:48.244 --> 25:51.010
It'll be over just like this.
"Oh, what's that?" [anaugulia]

25:51.611 --> 25:52.649
Trust me.

26:05.225 --> 26:07.561
You're gonna Old Yeller
my fucking universe?

26:07.696 --> 26:09.796
Mm... In your parlance, yes.

26:09.932 --> 26:11.228
Two in the heart,
one in the head.

26:11.363 --> 26:13.327
Angalia, Mr. Wilson,
you have two choices.

26:13.463 --> 26:14.867
You can either rejoin
your loved ones

26:15.003 --> 26:16.766
and collectively cease
to exist in,

26:16.902 --> 26:19.837
I'd say, 72 hours. Or...

26:19.973 --> 26:22.404
you join the Sacred Timeline.

26:22.539 --> 26:24.806
And you end your days
of insignificance

26:24.941 --> 26:27.082
and mediocrity.

26:27.217 --> 26:28.680
Wade.

26:28.815 --> 26:30.581
Wade, you can finally,

26:30.716 --> 26:33.250
hatimaye jambo.

26:37.423 --> 26:40.257
- [Hulk roars]
- [♪ kucheza muziki wa hisia]

26:42.865 --> 26:44.901
That's all
I've ever really wanted.

26:45.037 --> 26:46.428
I know.

26:46.929 --> 26:48.770
I know.

26:48.906 --> 26:50.967
And you know I'm...
I'm nothing if not

26:51.102 --> 26:52.500
morally flexible. [anacheka]

26:52.936 --> 26:54.139
[anacheka]

26:54.872 --> 26:56.075
Yep, yep.

26:58.073 --> 26:59.214
I'll do it.

26:59.349 --> 27:00.409
Wise choice.

27:00.544 --> 27:02.016
The Sacred Timeline's happy
to have you.

27:02.151 --> 27:03.280
[Deadpool] I was actually
talking about finding

27:03.416 --> 27:05.183
the Wolverine and breaking
your fucking nose.

27:05.948 --> 27:07.152
[anaugulia]

27:08.555 --> 27:09.994
[♪ soft rock music plays,
Goo Goo Dolls "Iris"]

27:10.129 --> 27:12.656
<i>♪ And I'd give up forever
to touch you ♪</i>

27:12.791 --> 27:16.727
<i>♪ 'Cause I know
that you feel me somehow ♪</i>

27:16.862 --> 27:18.064
[♪ kusimamishwa kwa wimbo]

27:18.865 --> 27:21.132
Find him. Find him!

27:21.267 --> 27:23.172
[Deadpool]
<i>And boy, did he ever.</i>

27:23.307 --> 27:24.837
[kuguna]

27:24.972 --> 27:26.501
<i>Which brings us back to this.</i>

27:28.440 --> 27:30.639
<i>The desecration
of the sacred corpse.</i>

27:30.775 --> 27:33.574
- [♪ dramatic kucheza muziki]
- [yelling and grunting]

27:34.849 --> 27:36.544
- Oh, Mungu wangu!
- [Anapiga kelele]

27:37.554 --> 27:40.487
Oh! My own fucking arm!

27:40.622 --> 27:41.690
[soldier 1 yells]

27:41.826 --> 27:43.485
- [soldier 1 screams]
- [kuguna]

27:43.620 --> 27:45.119
- [soldier 1 screaming]
- Now we're talkin'!

27:45.255 --> 27:46.658
[soldier 1] Not like this!

27:46.793 --> 27:48.864
No, dear God! Hapana!

27:49.000 --> 27:51.026
[Deadpool] I'm sorry!
Wolverine-ing is hard!

27:51.162 --> 27:52.467
[soldier 2] Make it stop!

27:52.603 --> 27:53.698
[Deadpool] Mangold tried.

27:53.834 --> 27:55.706
[soldiers screaming]

27:56.605 --> 27:58.571
You sick fuck!

27:58.706 --> 27:59.972
Logan was a hero.

28:00.107 --> 28:01.576
And the only thing
worth a shit

28:01.711 --> 28:03.077
to ever come out of Canada.

28:03.646 --> 28:04.605
[soldier 1 cries out]

28:05.208 --> 28:06.409
[soldier 2 screams]

28:10.855 --> 28:12.949
[Deadpool]
Get my country's name

28:13.085 --> 28:15.286
out of your fuckin' mouth.

28:16.187 --> 28:18.058
And my sword. Give me that.

28:20.331 --> 28:21.224
[hushusha pumzi]

28:21.359 --> 28:23.658
Oh, I gotta find me
another Logan.

28:24.094 --> 28:25.329
An alive one.

28:25.464 --> 28:28.334
Don't get up, guys.
I'll see myself out.

28:28.470 --> 28:31.203
[♪ synth rock music playing,
"The Power of Love"]

28:35.411 --> 28:36.406
Logan!

28:39.916 --> 28:41.719
I'm gonna need you
to come with me.

28:42.849 --> 28:44.051
Who's asking?

28:44.852 --> 28:46.054
[♪ muziki unasimama]

28:46.189 --> 28:48.021
[Deadpool] Oh, look at
this little Hairy Lou Retton.

28:48.157 --> 28:49.991
Did you stick the landing,
little guy?

28:50.560 --> 28:51.493
Yes, you did!

28:51.629 --> 28:53.187
Comic-accurate short king.

28:53.323 --> 28:55.630
Such a cute wittle Wolvie.

28:55.766 --> 28:57.295
Cue the fuckin' montage, baby.

28:57.430 --> 28:59.030
- [♪ synth rock music resumes]
- Ahoy!

28:59.165 --> 29:01.337
Everything seems
to be on fire.

29:01.472 --> 29:03.004
You have a dragon?

29:03.140 --> 29:05.604
Ooh, you have Anchor Being
written all over--

29:05.739 --> 29:07.470
[kuguna]

29:08.544 --> 29:09.937
[growling]

29:10.073 --> 29:13.248
<i>♪ Make a one man weep,
make another man sing ♪</i>

29:13.851 --> 29:15.382
<i>♪ Change a hawk...♪</i>

29:15.517 --> 29:16.544
Patch!

29:16.680 --> 29:19.757
- [engine revving]
- Oh, now we're talkin'.

29:20.457 --> 29:22.056
Oh, yeah.

29:22.191 --> 29:24.322
That's the whole goddamn
package right there.

29:25.329 --> 29:26.356
Howdy!

29:26.492 --> 29:28.932
I'm just... I'm auditioning
Anchor Beings.

29:29.067 --> 29:31.692
Oh. Yeah, that's gonna need
some coconut oil.

29:33.502 --> 29:34.534
[kuguna]

29:34.670 --> 29:35.866
[crow cawing]

29:36.001 --> 29:38.067
What in the fuck?

29:38.202 --> 29:39.976
[anacheka] Are you okay?

29:40.412 --> 29:41.337
Oh, yes, yes.

29:41.473 --> 29:43.242
Classic John Byrne
brown and tan.

29:43.377 --> 29:45.209
Now, you fought the Hulk
in this outfit. No?

29:45.345 --> 29:47.279
- [deep growl]
- [♪ wimbo unasimama]

29:48.216 --> 29:49.880
I'm Marvel Jesus,
you dull creature,

29:50.016 --> 29:51.251
and I will not-- [Anapiga kelele]

29:51.387 --> 29:52.680
- [Deadpool inaugulia]
- [♪ wimbo unaendelea kucheza]

29:53.589 --> 29:55.056
[kuguna]

29:57.994 --> 30:00.558
- [thunder rumbles]
- [kuomboleza]

30:00.694 --> 30:03.526
It's not you. We're just going
in a different direction.

30:05.535 --> 30:06.634
[engine revving]

30:06.769 --> 30:07.737
Unajua, from behind,

30:07.873 --> 30:08.870
you look a little bit
like Henry--

30:09.006 --> 30:10.300
- Oh, my fuck!
- [♪ wimbo unasimama]

30:10.436 --> 30:13.603
The Cavillrine.
The legends are true.

30:13.738 --> 30:16.644
And may I say, sir,
on behalf of all humanity,

30:16.779 --> 30:18.615
this just feels right.

30:18.751 --> 30:20.179
We will treat you
so much better

30:20.315 --> 30:21.511
than those shit fucks
down the street.

30:21.646 --> 30:23.821
- You were just leavin'.
- [Deadpool] No, sir.

30:23.956 --> 30:25.449
Not while the fate
of my universe is at--

30:27.722 --> 30:28.716
[man grunts]

30:29.284 --> 30:30.020
[kusonga]

30:30.156 --> 30:31.591
This one looks promising.

30:31.726 --> 30:33.028
Down you go.

30:34.466 --> 30:35.427
[Logan] Again.

30:36.297 --> 30:38.458
I told you.
You're not welcome here.

30:38.593 --> 30:39.933
You're not welcome anywhere.

30:40.068 --> 30:41.268
Now get the fuck
out of my bar.

30:41.403 --> 30:43.939
Just give me one more drink
and then I'll leave.

30:44.074 --> 30:45.765
[bartender] That's not
how it works.

30:45.901 --> 30:48.003
[Deadpool] It does now.
Leave the bottle.

30:48.138 --> 30:49.105
I know you, bub?

30:49.240 --> 30:51.711
Nope. Lakini I know you.

30:51.847 --> 30:53.312
Everybody knows me.

30:54.783 --> 30:55.813
I'm the Wolverine.

30:55.949 --> 30:58.219
Yes, you are.

30:58.354 --> 31:00.451
And I'm gonna need you
to come with me right now.

31:01.784 --> 31:03.089
Angalia, lady,
I'm not interested.

31:03.225 --> 31:04.526
Really gettin'
into your cups here.

31:04.662 --> 31:06.193
Why would I go with you?

31:07.159 --> 31:08.925
Because, unfortunately,

31:09.060 --> 31:10.364
I need you,

31:10.500 --> 31:14.499
and even more unfortunately,
my entire world needs you.

31:15.168 --> 31:16.731
You two gonna fuck or fight?

31:20.713 --> 31:22.039
You gonna take that from him?

31:22.175 --> 31:23.607
- Yep.
- [scoffs]

31:23.742 --> 31:25.772
I can tell you have a sort
of don't-get-too-close-

31:25.908 --> 31:27.583
I'll-only-break-your-heart
vibe going here,

31:27.719 --> 31:28.652
but every other Wolverine

31:28.787 --> 31:29.984
would've really hurt me
by now.

31:30.119 --> 31:31.218
And I'm sort of
on the tick-tick.

31:31.353 --> 31:32.721
- So, upsy-daisy. Here we go.
- Whoa, whoa.

31:32.857 --> 31:33.786
- Up you go.
- Hey, hey!

31:33.922 --> 31:35.123
I got you, big guy.

31:36.427 --> 31:37.422
Oh.

31:38.862 --> 31:39.963
Whiskey dick of the claws.

31:40.098 --> 31:41.530
It's quite common
in Wolverines over 40.

31:41.666 --> 31:42.757
You don't want this.

31:42.892 --> 31:45.230
You're right. I don't.
And you don't want this.

31:45.365 --> 31:46.834
Unless you wanna
take a deep breath

31:46.970 --> 31:48.065
through your fuckin' forehead,

31:48.201 --> 31:50.297
I suggest you reconsider.

31:50.432 --> 31:51.502
Let's go, peanut.

31:53.775 --> 31:55.809
[laughing]

31:55.945 --> 31:57.981
Hold on. Hold on. Hold on.

31:58.516 --> 31:59.510
Watch this.

32:00.509 --> 32:02.513
Sawa. That-- Whoa.

32:02.948 --> 32:04.152
Easy.

32:07.690 --> 32:09.123
Good God.

32:09.259 --> 32:11.258
Thirsty little honey badger,
aren't ya?

32:12.191 --> 32:13.820
It's okay. Keep goin'.

32:13.956 --> 32:16.032
Audiences are accustomed
to long run times.

32:16.930 --> 32:19.332
[grunts, groans]

32:19.933 --> 32:21.265
[body thuds]

32:21.400 --> 32:23.670
[anapumua]
Guess you'll have to do.

32:23.805 --> 32:25.008
Okay, here we--

32:25.975 --> 32:28.811
Oh! Look at those jammies.

32:28.947 --> 32:32.144
That only took
20 fucking years.

32:32.279 --> 32:34.440
One Anchor Being
coming right up!

32:34.576 --> 32:36.750
On your left, mtoto wa kike.

32:36.886 --> 32:37.955
This Logan has the same

32:38.090 --> 32:40.154
he-can-do-anything-
even-musicals look.

32:40.290 --> 32:42.254
And bonus, he's actually
wearing a costume

32:42.390 --> 32:43.517
like he's not
embarrassed to be

32:43.653 --> 32:44.923
in a superhero movie for once.

32:45.059 --> 32:46.586
I don't understand.

32:46.722 --> 32:47.889
You said my universe is dying

32:48.024 --> 32:50.297
because this sack of nuts
got himself killed.

32:50.432 --> 32:52.960
Well, problem solved.
<i>- </i> My God.

32:53.095 --> 32:57.407
You actually think you can
replace an Anchor Being

32:57.542 --> 32:59.407
with this?

32:59.543 --> 33:02.008
I wouldn't have accepted
any other Wolverine, BT dubs.

33:02.144 --> 33:04.045
Lakini you have outdone yourself

33:04.181 --> 33:06.211
and brought me
the worst Wolverine!

33:06.347 --> 33:07.516
What do you mean,
the worst one?

33:07.651 --> 33:09.018
Bw. Wilson.

33:09.154 --> 33:13.012
This Wolverine let down
his entire world.

33:13.148 --> 33:15.425
He's the stuff of legend,
but not in a good way.

33:15.560 --> 33:16.689
And what he did,

33:16.824 --> 33:18.094
well,

33:18.229 --> 33:20.525
some things are just
beyond forgiveness.

33:22.830 --> 33:24.157
Sawa.

33:24.293 --> 33:27.002
How do I... How do I make
this right? I'll do anything.

33:27.138 --> 33:29.996
I gave you
a chance at greatness.

33:30.131 --> 33:32.634
Because my superiors
deemed you "special."

33:32.769 --> 33:34.137
Clearly not special
in a good way.

33:34.273 --> 33:35.208
Apparently you have some

33:35.343 --> 33:37.404
important future purpose
to serve.

33:37.540 --> 33:38.515
With Thor. He holds me.

33:38.650 --> 33:40.346
Lakini I did my duty.

33:40.482 --> 33:42.413
I gave you the opportunity
to be somebody.

33:42.549 --> 33:44.418
And instead of
accepting my offering

33:44.553 --> 33:46.919
with humility and gratitude,
you broke my nose.

33:47.055 --> 33:48.023
[anapumua] It looks great.

33:48.159 --> 33:49.959
And you decimated
dozens of my men

33:50.094 --> 33:51.590
with the exhumed corpse
of a hero.

33:51.725 --> 33:53.961
Dishonoring not only
his remains but his memory.

33:54.096 --> 33:55.323
What are you, the Internet?

33:55.459 --> 33:57.600
Your world is dying!

33:57.736 --> 33:58.999
Thank you very much.

33:59.134 --> 34:00.433
And there's no stopping it.

34:02.470 --> 34:04.068
[muffled]
The humane thing to do

34:04.204 --> 34:05.206
is to make it quick.

34:05.341 --> 34:07.104
Is the thought
of vaporizing my universe

34:07.240 --> 34:08.402
making you peckish?

34:08.538 --> 34:09.840
I'm eating my feelings.

34:09.976 --> 34:11.214
I'm about to lose everything
that I've ever cared about

34:11.350 --> 34:14.374
because that hairy thundercunt
from down undercunt

34:14.510 --> 34:15.646
finally dies,

34:15.782 --> 34:17.987
and he's standing
right behind me, isn't he?

34:18.123 --> 34:19.989
Karibu kwa the MCU,
by the way.

34:20.125 --> 34:22.190
You're joining at a bit
of a low point.

34:22.326 --> 34:24.257
As for you,
I wanna talk to your boss.

34:24.393 --> 34:25.687
I want you to get him
on the phone

34:25.823 --> 34:27.722
and you tell him,
her, or them,

34:27.858 --> 34:30.166
that Marvel H. Christ
isn't playing.

34:35.464 --> 34:36.469
Holy shit.

34:37.138 --> 34:38.975
I just heard a symphony

34:39.111 --> 34:40.939
of buttholes clenching
all at once.

34:41.074 --> 34:42.178
You're off grid.

34:42.313 --> 34:43.536
Your bosses don't know
what you sick fucks

34:43.672 --> 34:44.604
are doing down here.

34:44.740 --> 34:45.773
Well, I'll tell you what.

34:45.909 --> 34:47.750
I have a black belt
in Karen...

34:47.886 --> 34:49.075
And I'm gonna go upstairs

34:49.210 --> 34:51.550
and I'm gonna tell 'em
all about you and your--

34:52.320 --> 34:54.020
Oh, silence is nice, isn't it?

34:54.156 --> 34:55.190
Where the fuck did he go?

34:55.326 --> 34:57.151
To the trash heap.
You'll fit right in.

34:57.287 --> 34:58.791
[hunguruma]

34:58.926 --> 35:00.125
Whew.

35:00.261 --> 35:01.725
That was close. [anacheka]

35:04.936 --> 35:07.368
[muffled rhythmic thumping]

35:10.975 --> 35:13.176
[muffled footsteps thumping]

35:17.308 --> 35:18.544
[kulalamika]

35:22.519 --> 35:24.984
[Deadpool] Don't just
stand there, you ape.

35:25.119 --> 35:27.057
Give me a hand up.

35:27.192 --> 35:28.985
- [claws clang]
- Nope. I'm actually okay.

35:29.120 --> 35:31.293
- Thank you very much. [anaugulia]
- [Wolverine grunting]

35:32.329 --> 35:33.394
[Wolverine]
Where the hell are we?

35:33.529 --> 35:35.857
[Deadpool] sijui.
Looks kind of Mad Max-y.

35:35.993 --> 35:37.897
Lakini that would be
IP infringement, right?

35:38.033 --> 35:39.166
Fucking jokes.

35:39.302 --> 35:40.933
- [kuguna]
- [Deadpool yelps]

35:41.069 --> 35:42.629
[bones crack]

35:42.764 --> 35:44.073
[Deadpool] Fuck! Fuck.

35:44.209 --> 35:45.572
Were you even listening
back there?

35:45.707 --> 35:48.570
If we don't make it back
to that Mr. Paradox asshole,

35:48.706 --> 35:49.943
everyone I know is gonna die.

35:50.079 --> 35:51.813
Not my fuckin' problem.

35:51.949 --> 35:53.977
Oh, is that all you got?

35:54.112 --> 35:56.286
Is that what you said
when your world went to shit?

35:57.156 --> 35:59.449
[kupumua sana]
Come again?

35:59.584 --> 36:01.484
Yeah, I heard all about you.

36:01.620 --> 36:03.584
How you screwed up everything.

36:03.720 --> 36:04.788
You should be thankin' me

36:04.923 --> 36:06.459
for pulling you out
of that bed you shit in.

36:06.595 --> 36:08.761
[anaugulia] You back-stabbing
mtoto wa mbwembwe!

36:08.897 --> 36:10.200
[kupiga kelele]

36:13.364 --> 36:14.761
[shouts, groans]

36:14.897 --> 36:16.137
Are you ready to be calm now?

36:16.273 --> 36:18.208
- [kuguna]
- [Deadpool yelps]

36:20.975 --> 36:22.179
[anaugulia]

36:23.378 --> 36:25.613
Rest in pieces, Fox. [kuguna]

36:25.749 --> 36:28.476
[♪ tense song intro playing,
AC/DC "Hells Bells"]

36:28.611 --> 36:30.319
[bird screeching]

36:40.528 --> 36:42.331
I don't want to fight you, peanut.

36:43.298 --> 36:44.958
Doesn't matter what you did.

36:45.093 --> 36:46.764
- I just need your help.
- [kuguna]

36:48.038 --> 36:49.701
I don't fuckin' care.

36:50.940 --> 36:52.808
Uh... Uh-oh.

36:52.943 --> 36:54.376
[breathes heavily]

36:58.313 --> 37:00.976
Fuck. This is gonna hurt.

37:04.921 --> 37:06.389
Sawa.

37:06.658 --> 37:08.115
Fuck it.

37:08.250 --> 37:10.051
Let's give the people
what they came for.

37:10.186 --> 37:12.988
- [♪ wimbo unasimama]
- Let's fuckin' go.

37:13.925 --> 37:15.930
Get your special sock out, nerds.

37:16.066 --> 37:18.125
It's gonna get good.

37:18.703 --> 37:20.028
[kuguna]

37:25.369 --> 37:26.806
[♪ hard rock music playing,
AC/DC "Hells Bells"]

37:26.942 --> 37:28.201
[hunguruma]

37:29.407 --> 37:30.709
[gunshots]

37:39.087 --> 37:40.686
[wote wawili wakiguna]

37:43.288 --> 37:44.294
[anaugulia]

37:50.868 --> 37:51.793
[mayowe]

37:51.928 --> 37:53.633
<i>♪ Hell's bells ♪</i>

37:55.574 --> 37:58.307
<i>♪ I'll give you
black sensations ♪</i>

37:58.442 --> 38:01.205
<i>♪ Up and down your spine ♪</i>

38:01.340 --> 38:04.781
<i>♪ If you're into evil,
you're a friend of mine ♪</i>

38:04.916 --> 38:08.042
<i>♪ See my white light flashing
as I split the night ♪</i>

38:08.178 --> 38:10.078
- [grunts, growls]
- [Deadpool inacheka] Ew.

38:10.920 --> 38:12.414
Gotcha!

38:12.550 --> 38:16.020
<i>♪ I got my bell, I'm gonna
take you to hell ♪</i>

38:16.156 --> 38:18.456
<i>♪ I'm gonna get you,
Satan get you ♪</i>

38:18.592 --> 38:20.154
- Kisu cha Mtoto!
- [anaomboleza]

38:23.928 --> 38:24.966
- [mayowe]
- Let's see you grow

38:25.102 --> 38:26.260
your fuckin' head back.

38:26.395 --> 38:28.096
Wait, wait, wait!
I can fix it! I can fix it.

38:28.231 --> 38:30.340
- Fix what?
- Whatever it is that you did.

38:31.109 --> 38:32.574
Whatever made you so bad.

38:33.010 --> 38:34.309
Those... Those

38:34.445 --> 38:37.007
pricks in the TVA.
Ulisikia him.

38:38.010 --> 38:39.140
They have the power
to end my universe,

38:39.276 --> 38:42.616
but they also have
the power to change yours.

38:44.182 --> 38:47.317
We get back there,
and we can fix your world.

38:47.452 --> 38:48.622
Together.

38:49.894 --> 38:51.152
I promise.

38:52.556 --> 38:53.759
They can fix it.

38:54.866 --> 38:56.065
[man] Hey!

38:56.201 --> 38:58.199
We fight each other, we lose.

38:58.335 --> 38:59.630
[Deadpool] Dear God, it's him.

38:59.765 --> 39:02.032
- Who?
- [Deadpool] The one.

39:02.167 --> 39:04.969
The superhero equivalent
to comfort food, or Molly.

39:05.104 --> 39:07.636
White guys' answer
to all the disappointments.

39:07.771 --> 39:08.977
And another A-lister.

39:09.113 --> 39:10.404
Fair warning, gorgeous.

39:10.539 --> 39:12.482
You're going to encounter
some indelicate language,

39:12.617 --> 39:15.051
a smidge of ass play,
but we've been prohibited

39:15.187 --> 39:16.947
from using cocaine. On camera.

39:17.083 --> 39:19.215
- [man] They're coming.
- [Deadpool] Who's "they"?

39:19.350 --> 39:21.721
- [engines revving]
- [♪ menacing kucheza muziki]

39:25.988 --> 39:27.529
Oh, they're driving angry.

39:32.496 --> 39:33.401
[kuguna]

39:33.536 --> 39:35.127
Now that's
a superhero landing.

39:35.263 --> 39:37.473
[♪ menacing music continues]

39:40.969 --> 39:42.273
[♪ muziki unasimama]

39:42.408 --> 39:43.509
I got this.

39:43.644 --> 39:45.646
[♪ menacing music resumes]

39:49.953 --> 39:51.146
[kunusa]

39:55.884 --> 39:57.317
[engines revving]

40:07.334 --> 40:08.467
Stay close.

40:08.602 --> 40:09.736
[Deadpool] Aye, aye, Cap'n.

40:11.042 --> 40:12.233
You got this.

40:14.307 --> 40:18.041
Cassandra ni gonna be giddy
when she sees what we caught.

40:18.874 --> 40:19.840
You can't run.

40:19.975 --> 40:21.142
Everybody knows that.

40:21.277 --> 40:23.576
You see anyone runnin',
dick for brains?

40:24.479 --> 40:26.218
You're not gonna love
what happens next.

40:26.353 --> 40:28.249
- [Deadpool] Oh. Oh, my God.
- [♪ rousing kucheza muziki]

40:28.384 --> 40:30.588
Oh, my God.
Oh, my God, he's gonna say it.

40:30.724 --> 40:31.655
- Ah! Fuck.
- [Deadpool] Ha!

40:31.791 --> 40:33.219
Oh, Mungu wangu! He's gonna say it!

40:33.355 --> 40:34.990
- Say what?
- Avengers, assemble...

40:35.126 --> 40:36.565
- Flame on!
- I'm sorry, what now?

40:38.962 --> 40:41.163
[♪ kucheza muziki wa ajabu]

40:52.677 --> 40:54.484
[groans, panting]

40:56.154 --> 40:58.350
[screaming in distance]

40:58.485 --> 40:59.756
- [clang]
- Ohh!

40:59.891 --> 41:01.120
Kumbe!

41:01.255 --> 41:02.250
Ahhh!

41:02.817 --> 41:04.022
[kuguna]

41:05.192 --> 41:07.391
- We don't know that guy.
- [Deadpool] We thought we did.

41:07.526 --> 41:09.499
I know you.

41:09.634 --> 41:11.666
- [Deadpool] Holy sh--
- [Sabretooth snarls]

41:12.299 --> 41:13.232
[hunguruma]

41:13.367 --> 41:14.362
Sabretooth.

41:14.798 --> 41:16.000
Your brother.

41:16.734 --> 41:18.399
Ready to die?

41:18.534 --> 41:21.203
[Deadpool] Wait, wait, wait,
wait, wait, wait! Time!

41:21.806 --> 41:23.303
You look ridiculous.

41:23.439 --> 41:25.975
People have waited decades
for this fight.

41:26.111 --> 41:27.878
It's not gonna be easy.
Baby Knife.

41:28.014 --> 41:29.812
Shoot the double,
you take him down.

41:29.948 --> 41:31.944
Side control, then full mount,

41:32.080 --> 41:33.347
and you ground and pound

41:33.482 --> 41:35.051
till he makes no sound
because he's dead.

41:35.187 --> 41:37.051
- Nyamaza jamani!
- [Deadpool] Oh, Mungu wangu!

41:37.187 --> 41:39.523
Sawa. Good luck.
I'm a huge fan.

41:39.659 --> 41:41.157
[kupumua sana]

41:42.659 --> 41:43.698
[anacheka]

41:44.793 --> 41:46.131
[roars]

41:46.267 --> 41:47.669
[roars]

41:51.676 --> 41:53.104
- [kuguna]
- [Deadpool] What is it, girl?

41:53.240 --> 41:55.138
- Is there trouble at the well?
- [mwili kunyoosha]

41:59.943 --> 42:01.509
[anacheka] Big trouble.

42:01.645 --> 42:03.209
Behold!

42:03.345 --> 42:06.448
The head
of your precious queen,

42:06.584 --> 42:07.590
Furiosa!

42:08.721 --> 42:10.455
I have the Wolverine!

42:10.591 --> 42:13.655
I alone control her!

42:13.790 --> 42:15.988
You come for me,

42:16.123 --> 42:18.634
you come for her.

42:20.232 --> 42:22.033
So sorry.
I know it's pronounced "him."

42:22.168 --> 42:23.940
I'm gender blind.
It's my cross to bear.

42:24.075 --> 42:25.404
Who's next?

42:25.540 --> 42:26.569
- Toad!
- [snarls]

42:26.704 --> 42:28.006
You're up.

42:30.608 --> 42:31.772
[kupiga kelele]

42:31.907 --> 42:33.077
[both grunt]

42:34.977 --> 42:35.911
[Deadpool] Uh-oh.

42:36.046 --> 42:37.315
- Oh, holy sh--
- Kumbe.

42:37.450 --> 42:38.445
[thud]

42:39.851 --> 42:41.756
[creatures squeaking]

42:46.155 --> 42:48.126
[Deadpool groans, mumbles]

42:48.762 --> 42:50.259
[Deadpool] God of Thunder.

42:51.796 --> 42:52.998
[Deadpool grunts]

42:54.063 --> 42:55.501
How long was I asleep?

42:55.637 --> 42:57.165
Not all of you was asleep.

42:57.301 --> 42:58.801
- [Miguno ya Deadpool]
- Don't bother.

42:58.936 --> 43:01.104
They're very thorough.

43:01.239 --> 43:03.470
If you know where we are,
start talking.

43:04.073 --> 43:05.643
You're in The Void.

43:05.779 --> 43:07.747
Think of it as purgatory.

43:07.883 --> 43:10.110
Reed called it
a metaphysical junkyard.

43:10.245 --> 43:11.718
Where anything useless goes

43:11.854 --> 43:13.954
before it gets
annihilated forever.

43:14.089 --> 43:16.822
And where the TVA sends
people that don't play nice

43:16.958 --> 43:17.985
with the rest
of the multiverse.

43:18.121 --> 43:19.760
- Like you?
- Na wewe.

43:19.896 --> 43:21.389
[Deadpool] What does
the annihilating?

43:21.857 --> 43:22.795
Alioth.

43:22.930 --> 43:24.258
[Deadpool]
Alioth is in this thing?

43:24.394 --> 43:26.361
From <i>Loki,</i>
Season 1, Episode 5?

43:26.496 --> 43:28.661
Everyone here
is on the run from Alioth.

43:29.197 --> 43:30.768
Most don't make it.

43:30.904 --> 43:32.840
There's a resistance, though.

43:32.975 --> 43:35.908
Other people like us
that managed to survive.

43:36.044 --> 43:37.306
They're hidin' out
in the borderlands,

43:37.441 --> 43:39.775
trying to find a way
the fuck outta here.

43:39.911 --> 43:41.174
Then that's where we go.

43:41.309 --> 43:43.178
[Deadpool] "We"? Us? A team?

43:43.313 --> 43:45.347
The answer is yes.
Shake on it.

43:45.950 --> 43:47.085
Kumbe! You nicked it.

43:47.220 --> 43:49.154
Just got the tip with
your little steak knife.

43:49.289 --> 43:51.358
These "others" can help us
get back to the TVA.

43:51.494 --> 43:52.426
Make 'em fix things.

43:52.561 --> 43:54.626
[laughs sardonically]

43:54.761 --> 43:56.126
Something funny, bub?

43:56.262 --> 43:57.924
She might have somethin'
to say about that.

43:58.059 --> 43:59.328
Who's "she"?

44:00.600 --> 44:01.700
Katika Utupu,

44:01.836 --> 44:03.530
wewe ni chakula cha Alioth

44:04.199 --> 44:06.134
au unamfanyia kazi.

44:06.269 --> 44:08.469
[♪ stirring kucheza muziki]

44:18.355 --> 44:19.414
[engine roars]

44:27.858 --> 44:29.226
[metal creaking]

44:30.027 --> 44:31.459
[heavy metallic thud]

44:38.902 --> 44:40.567
[engine roaring]

44:51.687 --> 44:54.020
[♪ tense kucheza muziki]

45:02.991 --> 45:04.364
[kuguna]

45:04.499 --> 45:05.658
[growls quietly]

45:06.467 --> 45:07.462
[kuguna]

45:18.508 --> 45:20.607
[Deadpool] Huh.
Paul Rudd finally aged.

45:21.544 --> 45:23.214
Oh, you must be
this year's Juggernaut.

45:23.349 --> 45:24.981
- Thank you.
- I'd keep your voices down.

45:25.116 --> 45:26.421
She don't like the chatter.

45:26.556 --> 45:27.757
She's gonna love you.

45:29.156 --> 45:31.354
[♪ slow dramatic
music building]

45:43.874 --> 45:45.507
[Deadpool] Is it...
Is that Charles?

45:45.642 --> 45:47.771
Habari... Hey, Chuck! It's us!

45:47.906 --> 45:49.145
That's not Chuck.

45:49.280 --> 45:50.472
Ah, shit.

45:51.847 --> 45:53.179
[Deadpool] Oh, ableism. Great.

45:53.314 --> 45:55.745
That's not gonna go over well
with the woke mob.

45:55.880 --> 45:57.818
A Wolverine.

45:57.954 --> 46:00.383
I wondered when
I'd get one of you.

46:00.986 --> 46:02.121
You're one of Xavier's.

46:02.256 --> 46:03.819
[Deadpool] You-You know him?
You know Chuck?

46:03.954 --> 46:05.327
Oh, I knew him.

46:05.462 --> 46:06.763
We shared a womb.

46:06.898 --> 46:08.957
Tried to strangle
the sly little fellow

46:09.093 --> 46:10.462
with my umbilical cord.

46:10.597 --> 46:13.898
[Deadpool] Amen. I've never
loved roommates. Mine's blind.

46:14.033 --> 46:15.601
Except she can see cocaine.

46:15.737 --> 46:17.072
For some... reason.

46:17.207 --> 46:20.242
You want to chime in,
Your Majesty? I'm dying here.

46:20.377 --> 46:21.336
Who are you?

46:21.472 --> 46:24.306
Charles Xavier's twin,
Cassandra Nova.

46:24.442 --> 46:25.942
- Bullshit!
- I was an anal birth.

46:26.077 --> 46:28.717
Hmm. You two are cute.

46:28.853 --> 46:30.380
I have a good feeling
about this.

46:33.218 --> 46:34.215
And I've been trying to catch

46:34.351 --> 46:36.419
this little firefly for years.

46:37.054 --> 46:38.620
Haven't I, Johnny?

46:38.755 --> 46:42.029
Aw... You picked the wrong
time to make new friends.

46:42.164 --> 46:44.427
[Deadpool] Oh, Johnny told us
all about you.

46:44.562 --> 46:45.998
- Maybe shut up now.
- Yeah, maybe don't--

46:46.133 --> 46:47.094
[Deadpool]
We're just talkin' here.

46:47.230 --> 46:48.265
Yeah, Johnny told us

46:48.401 --> 46:50.469
you're a psychotic
megalomaniacal asshole.

46:50.605 --> 46:54.239
His words, not mine.
Hellbent on domination
and pain.

46:55.206 --> 46:56.675
You said all that about me?

46:56.810 --> 46:58.410
Hapana! Hapana! I don't...

46:58.546 --> 47:00.740
- I didn't say any of that!
- Sticks and stones, Johnny!

47:02.247 --> 47:04.148
Don't let her intimidate you.

47:04.284 --> 47:06.051
It's like you said
in the convoy.

47:06.187 --> 47:08.022
This finger-lickin'
dead-inside

47:08.157 --> 47:10.958
pixie slab ya kiwango cha tatu
dime-store nut-milk

47:11.093 --> 47:12.828
can eat your delicious
cinnamon ring

47:12.963 --> 47:14.962
na piga mawe
njia yote ya kuzimu ya upara.

47:15.098 --> 47:17.065
Sawa. I have never said
any of those words

47:17.200 --> 47:19.229
- in my entire life!
- [Deadpool] Ha! The modesty.

47:19.364 --> 47:21.270
People think
I'm a shit talker.

47:21.405 --> 47:22.405
Lakini this guy...

47:22.540 --> 47:23.537
[smooches] Next level.

47:23.673 --> 47:25.698
Je! This... I... We...

47:25.834 --> 47:27.074
I don't even know
what half of that means!

47:27.209 --> 47:28.840
- This... I...
- My hat's off to you, sir.

47:28.976 --> 47:29.910
- Truly.
- Je! This...

47:30.045 --> 47:31.907
I didn't... He's...
That's... I...

47:32.043 --> 47:33.539
I... I don't--

47:33.675 --> 47:35.577
- [Deadpool inataabika]
- [heart beats]

47:38.714 --> 47:39.719
[Deadpool]
Not my favorite Chris.

47:39.855 --> 47:41.118
You stupid piece of shit.

47:41.254 --> 47:42.219
You just got him
fucking killed!

47:42.355 --> 47:44.125
[Deadpool] Hey!
We're all grieving!

47:44.260 --> 47:46.427
PS, do you know what
he was doing to the budget?

47:46.562 --> 47:47.754
[shushing]

47:49.060 --> 47:51.527
Alioth is hungry.

47:51.662 --> 47:53.230
[Deadpool] There's been
some kind of mistake.

47:53.366 --> 47:55.234
Big yellow is
a back-up Anchor Being,

47:55.369 --> 47:57.902
and I'm Marvel Jesus.
MJ, if you're nasty.

47:58.038 --> 47:58.972
This may be hard to hear,

47:59.108 --> 48:00.699
but there's
another British villain

48:00.835 --> 48:01.839
who's gonna destroy
my universe,

48:01.975 --> 48:03.010
and I'm gonna stop him.

48:03.145 --> 48:04.546
Oh, honey,
you don't really strike me

48:04.682 --> 48:06.278
as the world-saving type.

48:07.180 --> 48:08.549
[thunder rumbling in distance]

48:08.684 --> 48:10.414
Did I hit a nerve?

48:10.550 --> 48:12.251
[Deadpool] I didn't want it
to come to this.

48:12.886 --> 48:13.822
Either you help us

48:13.958 --> 48:15.187
or my friend here
is gonna sing

48:15.323 --> 48:17.019
the entire second act
of <i>Music Man</i>

48:17.154 --> 48:18.389
with zero warm-up.

48:19.092 --> 48:20.257
Where'd you get the chair?

48:20.393 --> 48:21.324
[Cassandra Nova]
Well, once in a while,

48:21.460 --> 48:23.388
I do get a Charles
through here.

48:23.524 --> 48:24.831
Never mine, though.

48:24.967 --> 48:28.037
Hapana. He didn't care to find me.

48:28.172 --> 48:31.636
[Deadpool groans] Gen Z
and their trauma-bragging!

48:31.771 --> 48:34.610
Can't you just stuff it down,
turn it into accomplishment

48:34.746 --> 48:36.239
or cancer like the rest of us?

48:36.374 --> 48:38.108
Lakini I'm not like
the rest of you.

48:38.243 --> 48:40.014
Except maybe the Wolverine.

48:40.150 --> 48:42.715
Now, we could be
truly terrifying together.

48:42.851 --> 48:44.048
You're that scary, huh?

48:44.184 --> 48:46.383
The TVA certainly thought so.

48:46.519 --> 48:49.055
They sent me here
before I could walk.

48:49.191 --> 48:50.559
And unajua,
it's the best thing

48:50.695 --> 48:52.361
that ever happened to me.

48:52.496 --> 48:53.522
I love it here.

48:53.658 --> 48:54.888
[Deadpool] You live
in a garbage dump.

48:55.024 --> 48:58.027
I think we both know who lives
in the garbage dump.

48:58.163 --> 48:59.902
The Void is a paradise.

49:00.037 --> 49:04.038
I can wield my power here
without shame.

49:04.174 --> 49:06.035
Unfortunately I had
no Charles Xavier

49:06.171 --> 49:08.037
to teach me temperance.

49:08.173 --> 49:10.039
What about your Charles?

49:10.175 --> 49:11.476
Did he protect you?

49:12.112 --> 49:14.145
Did he make you feel safe?

49:14.281 --> 49:16.114
We're mutants.
We're never safe.

49:16.250 --> 49:18.615
- [roars]
- [Cassandra whoops]

49:18.984 --> 49:20.154
[anacheka]

49:20.556 --> 49:21.617
[whoops]

49:24.326 --> 49:25.256
[Deadpool] Lo, wee,
wauu, wah!

49:25.391 --> 49:27.060
I don't...
I don't want the smoke.

49:27.195 --> 49:28.259
I don't have
any beef with you.

49:28.395 --> 49:29.896
I just want
to save my friends.

49:30.031 --> 49:31.198
I just... I want to go home.

49:31.333 --> 49:33.065
Well, the thing is,
I could get you home.

49:33.200 --> 49:34.870
- Good.
- Lakini I don't want to.

49:35.005 --> 49:37.270
[Deadpool] Not good.
[kulalamika]

49:39.668 --> 49:42.100
What do you want, Wade Wilson?

49:42.236 --> 49:44.646
[Deadpool straining] Your...
fingers are inside me,

49:44.781 --> 49:45.972
but not in a good way.

49:46.107 --> 49:48.882
My brother could enter
one's mind with a thought.

49:49.018 --> 49:51.216
I have to get my hands dirty.

49:51.352 --> 49:53.649
- [Deadpool groaning]
- [shushing]

49:54.383 --> 49:55.651
Nimekupata.

49:57.994 --> 49:59.391
[whispers] <i>Nimekupata...</i>

50:01.791 --> 50:03.032
[Wade, muffled]
<i>What do you mean?</i>

50:04.664 --> 50:07.403
I can't... I can't reach you.
You're not here.

50:07.538 --> 50:09.104
I'm right here.

50:09.240 --> 50:12.105
- No, you're not. I can't...
- I'm right here.

50:12.241 --> 50:14.439
Then show me.
You got to do something.

50:15.679 --> 50:17.003
Show you what?

50:17.138 --> 50:20.876
Show me you care about
something bigger than you.

50:21.011 --> 50:25.044
<i>Ever since they turned you
down, you took a knee.</i>

50:25.713 --> 50:27.683
Baby, you never got back up.

50:29.852 --> 50:31.617
I know you're
going through something.

50:31.753 --> 50:34.528
Let me go through it with you.

50:34.664 --> 50:37.066
