01:44:56.117 --> 01:44:57.280
[Deadpool] Kinyago
inatisha kweli, huh?

01:44:57.415 --> 01:44:59.484
Ni kama Batman,
isipokuwa anaweza kuisogeza shingo yake.

01:44:59.620 --> 01:45:01.218
Sawa, angalia, angalia, angalia.

01:45:02.421 --> 01:45:04.892
Ripper inalishwa kutoka
chumba salama chini ya ardhi.

01:45:05.028 --> 01:45:07.957
Inaendeshwa na vitu pacha
na malisho ya kuzuia vitu

01:45:08.092 --> 01:45:09.429
<i>kuunganishwa ndani ya kifaa.</i>

01:45:09.565 --> 01:45:10.633
<i>Sasa, Cassandra Nova</i>

01:45:10.768 --> 01:45:11.965
<i>inaelekeza kwingine
nguvu ya Ripper</i>

01:45:12.100 --> 01:45:13.997
kuondoa muda wote,
kuanzia na huyu.

01:45:14.133 --> 01:45:15.398
Kinadharia,
unaweza kumzuia

01:45:15.533 --> 01:45:17.401
kwa kusambaza malisho kwa muda mfupi
katika chumba cha chini.

01:45:17.536 --> 01:45:20.039
Mmoja wenu alikuwa atengeneze a
mzunguko kati ya malisho mawili,

01:45:20.174 --> 01:45:23.306
kisha nguvu iliyotolewa
itaharibu mashine.

01:45:23.441 --> 01:45:25.175
- Lakini, vizuri ... Lakini--
- [Deadpool] Njoo, mtu.

01:45:25.310 --> 01:45:27.310
Ikiwa hautameza,
mate nje.

01:45:27.445 --> 01:45:30.680
Yeyote aliyeunda daraja
ingeangamizwa.

01:45:30.816 --> 01:45:32.151
Ningeweza kuishi na hilo.

01:45:32.287 --> 01:45:33.525
[Deadpool] Ndio, ningeweza kuishi
na hilo, pia, kwa kweli.

01:45:33.661 --> 01:45:34.922
Unajua, tunaishi chochote.
Sisi ni kama mende.

01:45:35.058 --> 01:45:35.886
- [Deadpool inacheka]
- [Mr. Kitendawili] Sio wakati huu.

01:45:36.021 --> 01:45:38.264
Hili ni jambo
na kupinga jambo.

01:45:38.399 --> 01:45:40.323
Hawachezi vizuri
na kila mmoja.

01:45:40.459 --> 01:45:43.831
Wanapochanganyika katika mwili wako,
utakuwa atomized.

01:45:43.967 --> 01:45:45.933
Amini sheria za fizikia
kama huniamini.

01:45:46.069 --> 01:45:48.104
Hata kama uliishi muda wa kutosha
kutengeneza mzunguko,

01:45:48.240 --> 01:45:51.069
utafia huko chini.

01:45:56.576 --> 01:45:57.713
[kupasuka]

01:46:05.283 --> 01:46:07.584
[♪ kwaya ya kuigiza
kucheza muziki]

01:46:07.719 --> 01:46:09.120
[kuomboleza]

01:46:16.170 --> 01:46:17.632
[Wolverine] Acha. Shikilia.

01:46:17.768 --> 01:46:19.164
Ulisikia
yule mpuuzi pale juu.

01:46:19.300 --> 01:46:23.903
Hata kama tutaondoa hii,
tumekufa. Kudumu.

01:46:24.038 --> 01:46:26.269
- Ndio maana inabidi kuwa mimi.
- Je!

01:46:29.974 --> 01:46:31.909
Angalia, mtu ... [ akihema]

01:46:32.044 --> 01:46:34.281
hukuuliza
kwa lolote kati ya haya.

01:46:34.416 --> 01:46:35.654
Ulikuwa sahihi.

01:46:35.790 --> 01:46:36.983
Nilidanganya.

01:46:37.686 --> 01:46:39.249
Nilidanganya mbele ya uso wako

01:46:39.384 --> 01:46:41.493
ili tu unisaidie.
Na ulifanya.

01:46:42.424 --> 01:46:43.990
Hukudanganya.

01:46:45.793 --> 01:46:47.290
Ulifanya hamu ya elimu.

01:46:50.365 --> 01:46:51.360
Njoo.

01:46:52.363 --> 01:46:54.363
Una ulimwengu mzima
kurudi nyuma.

01:46:55.867 --> 01:46:57.069
Sikupata chochote.

01:46:59.013 --> 01:47:00.204
Sikupata chochote.

01:47:05.052 --> 01:47:06.243
Nipe hii.

01:47:13.289 --> 01:47:14.460
Habari.

01:47:18.863 --> 01:47:20.730
Nilisubiri kwa muda mrefu
kwa timu hii.

01:47:22.961 --> 01:47:24.228
Unajua kitu?

01:47:25.965 --> 01:47:27.563
Ulikuwa Wolverine bora zaidi.

01:47:28.332 --> 01:47:30.542
[♪ kucheza muziki wa hisia]

01:47:36.240 --> 01:47:38.275
Sema salamu kwa marafiki zako kwa ajili yangu.

01:47:46.951 --> 01:47:48.219
[Wolverine anaguna]

01:47:50.458 --> 01:47:51.391
Hapana!

01:47:51.527 --> 01:47:52.897
Fungua mlango!

01:47:53.032 --> 01:47:55.158
[Deadpool] Siwezi kukusikia
juu ya dhabihu zote adhimu.

01:47:55.294 --> 01:47:56.798
Kwa nini wewe
jamani kufanya hivi?

01:47:56.933 --> 01:48:00.033
[Deadpool]
Kwa sababu Mimi nina Ajabu Yesu.

01:48:01.602 --> 01:48:02.607
Au Spock.

01:48:03.802 --> 01:48:04.734
Vigumu kusema.

01:48:04.869 --> 01:48:06.204
[glasi inasikika]

01:48:07.476 --> 01:48:08.580
[smooches]

01:48:09.512 --> 01:48:10.807
[Wolverine] Wade!

01:48:10.942 --> 01:48:13.112
Mjinga wewe!

01:48:16.988 --> 01:48:19.688
[Deadpool inacheka]
Samahani, ninasitasita tu.

01:48:19.824 --> 01:48:21.725
Nadhani nina wasiwasi
kuhusu kufa.

01:48:22.591 --> 01:48:24.124
Huyu anapaswa kuwa mimi.

01:48:24.259 --> 01:48:25.954
[Deadpool] Msalimie
marafiki zangu kwa ajili yangu, karanga.

01:48:26.089 --> 01:48:27.359
[Wolverine] Wade!

01:48:27.494 --> 01:48:29.293
Unataka kuwa
pigo la kuudhi,
fanya upande huu!

01:48:29.428 --> 01:48:31.564
Utakufa huko,
mjinga wewe!

01:48:31.700 --> 01:48:33.198
[kupumua sana]

01:48:38.436 --> 01:48:40.404
Habari! Huna haja
kufanya hivi.

01:48:40.539 --> 01:48:42.438
[Deadpool] Sifanyi hivyo
kwa sababu ninaihitaji.

01:48:43.241 --> 01:48:45.443
Ninaifanya
kwa sababu wanafanya.

01:48:45.579 --> 01:48:46.717
[kuguna]

01:48:48.979 --> 01:48:50.754
[kukaza]

01:48:56.425 --> 01:48:57.629
Hapana!

01:48:58.560 --> 01:48:59.697
[kuguna]

01:49:01.827 --> 01:49:03.393
[kukaza]

01:49:11.308 --> 01:49:12.336
[kuguna]

01:49:14.004 --> 01:49:15.614
[kukaza]

01:49:22.012 --> 01:49:23.380
[hushusha pumzi]

01:49:24.148 --> 01:49:25.415
[anaendelea kukaza mwendo]

01:49:26.887 --> 01:49:28.484
Hatafanikiwa.

01:49:31.890 --> 01:49:33.258
[matatizo]

01:49:37.071 --> 01:49:38.329
Imekwisha.

01:49:40.007 --> 01:49:41.200
[kuguna]

01:49:41.900 --> 01:49:43.235
[kukaza]

01:49:46.511 --> 01:49:48.075
[anaendelea kukaza mwendo]

01:49:50.909 --> 01:49:52.113
[kupiga kelele]

01:49:52.248 --> 01:49:53.244
[kwaya]
<i>♪ Unapoita jina langu ♪</i>

01:49:53.379 --> 01:49:54.981
<i>♪ Ni kama maombi kidogo ♪</i>

01:49:55.117 --> 01:49:57.083
<i>♪ Nimepiga magoti ♪</i>

01:49:57.219 --> 01:49:59.355
<i>♪ nataka kukupeleka huko ♪</i>

01:49:59.490 --> 01:50:03.293
<i>♪ Saa ya usiku wa manane
Naweza kuhisi nguvu zako ♪</i>

01:50:03.428 --> 01:50:06.559
<i>♪ Kama maombi
Unajua nitakupeleka huko ♪</i>

01:50:06.694 --> 01:50:07.729
[kuguna]

01:50:07.865 --> 01:50:09.665
<i>♪ kukupeleka huko ♪</i>

01:50:09.801 --> 01:50:13.770
<i>♪ Maisha ni fumbo ♪</i>

01:50:13.905 --> 01:50:16.701
<i>♪ Kila mtu lazima asimame peke yake ♪</i>

01:50:16.836 --> 01:50:18.470
[kukaza]

01:50:18.606 --> 01:50:22.177
<i>- ♪ Nasikia ukiita jina langu ♪</i>
- [kuguna]

01:50:22.313 --> 01:50:24.276
<i>- ♪ Na inahisi kama ♪</i>
- [kukaza]

01:50:26.614 --> 01:50:30.517
<i>- ♪ Na inahisi kama nyumbani ♪</i>
- [kukaza]

01:50:30.652 --> 01:50:32.152
[kuunguruma]

01:50:38.759 --> 01:50:40.325
[kupiga kelele]

01:50:40.794 --> 01:50:42.393
[kupiga kelele]

01:50:44.470 --> 01:50:45.568
[♪ muziki hufifia]

01:50:45.703 --> 01:50:47.167
[Deadpool] <i>Wolverine.</i>

01:50:48.035 --> 01:50:50.071
<i>Yeye ni shujaa katika ulimwengu wangu.</i>

01:50:52.110 --> 01:50:53.135
[Wolverine] <i>Yeyote
unafikiri mimi ni,</i>

01:50:53.270 --> 01:50:54.713
<i>umepata mtu mbaya.</i>

01:50:56.147 --> 01:50:58.112
[Laura] <i>Ulikuwa daima
mtu mbaya...</i>

01:50:59.551 --> 01:51:00.485
<i>mpaka haukuwa.</i>

01:51:00.621 --> 01:51:02.947
<i>♪ Maisha ni fumbo ♪</i>

01:51:03.083 --> 01:51:04.381
[Bw. Kitendawili] <i>Wade.</i>

01:51:04.516 --> 01:51:06.417
<i>♪ Kila mtu lazima asimame peke yake ♪</i>

01:51:06.552 --> 01:51:10.926
<i>Wade. Unaweza hatimaye,
hatimaye jambo.</i>

01:51:11.061 --> 01:51:13.091
<i>♪ Nasikia ukiita jina langu ♪</i>

01:51:13.226 --> 01:51:17.670
<i>♪ Na inahisi kama ♪</i>

01:51:18.604 --> 01:51:22.338
<i>♪ Nyumbani ♪</i>

01:51:22.473 --> 01:51:23.673
[kukaza]

01:51:23.809 --> 01:51:26.736
<i>♪ Nasikia sauti yako ♪</i>

01:51:26.872 --> 01:51:28.041
Vanessa.

01:51:28.177 --> 01:51:30.546
<i>♪ Ni kama malaika anayeugua ♪</i>

01:51:30.682 --> 01:51:32.083
<i>Nataka kumuona Vanessa.</i>

01:51:32.219 --> 01:51:36.213
<i>♪ Sina chaguo
Nasikia sauti yako ♪</i>

01:51:36.349 --> 01:51:38.452
<i>♪ Anahisi kama kuruka ♪</i>

01:51:38.588 --> 01:51:43.157
Kwa mara ya kwanza maishani mwangu,
Ninajivunia kuvaa suti hii.

01:51:44.123 --> 01:51:46.061
<i>Ina maana mimi ni X-Man.</i>

01:51:48.466 --> 01:51:49.833
Mimi ndiye X-Man.

01:51:49.968 --> 01:51:51.764
<i>♪ Ninaweza kuhisi nguvu zako ♪</i>

01:51:51.899 --> 01:51:55.503
<i>♪ Kama maombi
Unajua nitakupeleka huko ♪</i>

01:51:55.638 --> 01:51:57.242
[kupiga kelele]

01:51:57.378 --> 01:52:00.073
<i>♪ Unapoita jina langu
Ni kama maombi kidogo ♪</i>

01:52:00.209 --> 01:52:02.609
<i>♪ Nimepiga magoti ♪</i>

01:52:02.744 --> 01:52:04.282
[kupiga kelele]

01:52:04.417 --> 01:52:08.146
<i>♪ Saa ya usiku wa manane
Naweza kuhisi nguvu zako ♪</i>

01:52:08.282 --> 01:52:09.815
<i>♪ Kama tu maombi ♪</i>

01:52:09.950 --> 01:52:13.759
<i>♪ Unajua nitakuchukua,
kukuchukua, kukuchukua ♪</i>

01:52:16.090 --> 01:52:17.389
[♪ wimbo unaisha]

01:52:24.638 --> 01:52:26.629
[♪ kucheza muziki makini]

01:52:33.973 --> 01:52:35.605
[mwanamke] Kitendawili.

01:52:37.450 --> 01:52:38.779
Umekuwa na shughuli nyingi.

01:52:38.915 --> 01:52:40.116
Naam, ilibidi mtu awe.

01:52:40.251 --> 01:52:41.949
Tulikuwa na usomaji wa ajabu
kutoka eneo hili.

01:52:42.085 --> 01:52:43.183
Usingejua
chochote kuhusu

01:52:43.319 --> 01:52:45.723
Kinasa sauti kisichoidhinishwa,
ungependa?

01:52:45.859 --> 01:52:47.351
Lo, hapana. Hapana.
Nisingejua chochote

01:52:47.487 --> 01:52:49.056
kuhusu asiyeidhinishwa
Wakati Ripper.

01:52:49.192 --> 01:52:50.791
Labda unapaswa kuuliza
Cassandra Nova.

01:52:50.926 --> 01:52:51.995
Kwa sababu nilikuwa na uhakika

01:52:52.130 --> 01:52:54.393
kwamba amehifadhiwa salama
katika Utupu. Lakini hapana,

01:52:54.528 --> 01:52:56.662
alikuwa hapa.
Na yeye aliupenda ubongo wangu.

01:52:56.798 --> 01:52:58.967
- Uliruhusuje hii kutokea?
- Hukuhusika hata kidogo?

01:52:59.103 --> 01:53:01.703
Katika kumzuia, ndiyo!
Ndiyo, nilikuwa.

01:53:01.838 --> 01:53:03.272
Lakini si karibu kutosha.

01:53:03.407 --> 01:53:05.778
Sio kama wanaume
ambaye alishuka huko nyuma yake.

01:53:06.510 --> 01:53:07.571
Wanaume wangu.

01:53:08.381 --> 01:53:09.375
Rafiki zangu.

01:53:10.681 --> 01:53:12.006
Niliwaonya.

01:53:12.142 --> 01:53:13.243
Kwamba wangekuwa kabisa
kufutwa kama walikwenda.

01:53:13.379 --> 01:53:15.117
Lakini walikwenda hata hivyo. Kama...

01:53:16.752 --> 01:53:18.051
Kama mashujaa.

01:53:18.186 --> 01:53:19.788
[♪ kucheza muziki mkali]

01:53:19.924 --> 01:53:21.651
Kwa sababu ndivyo walivyokuwa.

01:53:24.359 --> 01:53:26.095
Walifanya tu
walichopaswa kufanya.

01:53:27.230 --> 01:53:29.098
Bila wasiwasi
kwa usalama wao wenyewe.

01:53:32.401 --> 01:53:35.838
Ukweli kwamba sisi ni
wote bado wamesimama hapa

01:53:35.974 --> 01:53:38.767
ni agano
kwa ushujaa wao.

01:53:42.344 --> 01:53:43.645
Hata hivyo, hakuna kitu
wewe au mimi tunaweza kufanya

01:53:43.781 --> 01:53:45.015
kuwarudisha sasa.

01:53:46.479 --> 01:53:48.483
[Deadpool] Amefufuka,
mtoto wa kike.

01:53:48.618 --> 01:53:49.979
Kumbe!

01:53:50.114 --> 01:53:54.083
<i>♪ Na sitaki
ulimwengu kuniona ♪</i>

01:53:54.219 --> 01:53:58.988
<i>♪ Kwa sababu sidhani
kwamba wangeelewa ♪</i>

01:53:59.124 --> 01:54:03.135
<i>♪ Wakati kila kitu kiko
kufanywa kuvunjwa ♪</i>

01:54:03.270 --> 01:54:08.939
<i>♪ nakutaka wewe tu
kujua mimi ni nani ♪</i>

01:54:09.075 --> 01:54:10.205
[Deadpool]
Nimepata Nakala yako mpya.

01:54:10.341 --> 01:54:13.011
Na tunaendelea vizuri,
wewe kipande cha shit.

01:54:13.146 --> 01:54:14.576
- [wakala wa TVA wa kike] Mm.
- [wakala wa kiume wa TVA] Mm-hmm.

01:54:14.711 --> 01:54:16.080
Nzuri kweli.

01:54:16.215 --> 01:54:18.977
[Deadpool] Sawa.
Ondoa matiti yako yenye mafuta,

01:54:19.112 --> 01:54:20.080
wewe mchumba.

01:54:20.215 --> 01:54:22.587
- [anapumua]
- Sielewi.

01:54:22.722 --> 01:54:24.112
nyie wawili bado mko hai?

01:54:24.248 --> 01:54:25.954
[Deadpool] Ulikuwa sahihi. Moja
wetu tungeuawa.

01:54:26.090 --> 01:54:27.789
- [kukata tamaa]
- Lakini unaweka Deadpool

01:54:27.925 --> 01:54:29.159
na Wolverine pamoja,

01:54:29.295 --> 01:54:31.563
wafanye washike mikono
nikimsikiliza Madonna...

01:54:31.699 --> 01:54:34.032
asiyeweza kuharibika, mama mzazi.

01:54:34.167 --> 01:54:36.130
Wacha tuchukue Deadpool hii
Lahaja nyuma kwa The Void.

01:54:36.266 --> 01:54:37.458
[Deadpool] Subiri, shikilia.
Je!

01:54:37.594 --> 01:54:38.526
[Peter] Hapana. Kweli...

01:54:38.662 --> 01:54:40.305
Huyu ni mtu wa nyumbani kama mimi.

01:54:40.440 --> 01:54:41.636
Yeye ni wa hapa.

01:54:41.771 --> 01:54:42.764
Na wewe ni?

01:54:42.899 --> 01:54:45.570
Peterpool.
Lakini unaweza kuniita Peter.

01:54:47.075 --> 01:54:48.375
Na natumai utafanya.

01:54:54.482 --> 01:54:56.015
Nini jamani
inafanyika hapa?

01:54:56.150 --> 01:54:57.879
Uko chini ya hukumu

01:54:58.014 --> 01:54:59.923
kwa uendeshaji
Kinasa Muda kisichoidhinishwa.

01:55:00.059 --> 01:55:01.120
- Mchukue.
- Nilikuwa nikifanya nini

01:55:01.256 --> 01:55:02.757
huna
ujasiri wa kufanya.

01:55:02.893 --> 01:55:03.895
[Moshi wa Deadpool]

01:55:04.030 --> 01:55:06.756
Pata mikono yako ya jeuri
mbali yangu! Shuka!

01:55:07.964 --> 01:55:09.693
Ninashukuru, mabwana.

01:55:10.571 --> 01:55:11.762
Hebu tushike pinde.

01:55:11.897 --> 01:55:14.103
Uliongoza mutant ya kiwango cha Omega
kwa ratiba hii.

01:55:14.238 --> 01:55:15.797
- [Deadpool] Unakaribishwa.
- Na wewe

01:55:15.933 --> 01:55:17.303
haipaswi hata kuwa
karibu na kalenda hii ya matukio.

01:55:17.439 --> 01:55:19.611
- [Deadpool] Anakaribishwa.
- Na wewe

01:55:19.746 --> 01:55:21.478
angalia vizuri kwenye hiyo suti.

01:55:21.614 --> 01:55:22.706
samahani sana.

01:55:23.483 --> 01:55:24.576
[kifaa kinapiga]

01:55:27.083 --> 01:55:28.712
Nataka kukuonyesha kitu.

01:55:29.786 --> 01:55:31.046
Kitu kikubwa.

01:55:31.181 --> 01:55:33.057
[Deadpool] Hiyo ni nini
Skauti Kevin aliwahi kusema.

01:55:34.560 --> 01:55:36.023
Je, unaona hilo?

01:55:36.159 --> 01:55:38.029
Ulimwengu wako unazaa upya.

01:55:38.896 --> 01:55:40.555
Chochote ulichofanya hapa,

01:55:40.691 --> 01:55:42.900
hukuokoa ulimwengu wako tu.

01:55:43.036 --> 01:55:45.531
Umehifadhi rekodi yako ya matukio
kutoka kwa kutoweka.

01:55:47.397 --> 01:55:48.734
Ningepumzika.

01:55:48.870 --> 01:55:50.941
Ninahisi kazi yako
ndio inaanza tu.

01:55:51.077 --> 01:55:53.301
[Deadpool inanong'ona]
Mpaka una miaka 90.

01:55:53.436 --> 01:55:55.071
Subiri! Um...

01:55:55.206 --> 01:55:58.676
Hatukuweza kufaulu
ya The Void bila msaada wowote

01:55:58.811 --> 01:56:01.650
kutoka kwa baadhi ya watu
kwamba aina ya ulimwengu ...

01:56:01.785 --> 01:56:02.978
aina ya kusahau.

01:56:03.113 --> 01:56:05.622
Je, kuna njia yoyote hiyo
labda utapata njia

01:56:05.758 --> 01:56:07.091
kuwaleta nyumbani?

01:56:08.695 --> 01:56:09.919
Nitaona ninachoweza kufanya.

01:56:10.054 --> 01:56:12.458
[Deadpool] Na, um,
Nilimuahidi rafiki yangu hapa

01:56:12.594 --> 01:56:15.257
ambayo TVA inaweza kutengua
uchafu fulani mbaya sana

01:56:15.392 --> 01:56:16.162
katika ratiba yake.

01:56:16.297 --> 01:56:17.666
Ungesema nini kwa hilo?

01:56:17.801 --> 01:56:19.202
Badilisha zamani?

01:56:19.337 --> 01:56:21.501
